    <h1>Privacy Policy</h1>
    <p class="date">Last updated: March 23, 2025</p>
    
    <h2>Information We Collect</h2>
    <p>VibeCode Studio does not collect any personal information. The app only accesses files and folders that you explicitly select through the file picker. These file paths are stored locally as security-scoped bookmarks solely to provide the functionality of the app.</p>
    
    <h2>Data Storage</h2>
    <p>All data processed by VibeCode Studio remains on your device. We do not transmit any data to external servers.</p>
    
